(30057, 'eszopiclone', 'N/A', 'minor', 'When eszopiclone was coadministered with olanzapine, no pharmacokinetic interaction was detected in levels of eszopiclone or olanzapine, but a pharmacodynamic interaction was seen on a measure of psychomotor function.', 'DailyMed');
