(32234, 'fluoxetine hydrochloride', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Olanzapine – Fluoxetine (60 mg single dose or 60 mg daily dose for 8 days) causes a small (mean 16%) increase in the maximum concentration of olanzapine and a small (mean 16%) decrease in olanzapine clearance.', 'DailyMed'),
